  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was inspired by my tragic insomnia experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play cards at night to fall asleep as quick as possible, and enhance your deck by joining activities. Switch cards you have between deck and backups to build the perfect deck to overcome insomnia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a Single Player Rougelike Deckbuilder includes 1 playable character. Player's goal is to reduce their soberness at Night by spending time to play cards. Player can also use stamina joining Activities to gain more cards and advantages at the Daytime after every Night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also face even more Challenge in Deep Dream Mode where game gets harder everyday!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect various cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/3c921834216a30ee8faf03552f5cb368.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/3c921834216a30ee8faf03552f5cb368.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer Insomnia </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/680d979b647cbc16ed9d1acdb5a201c5.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/680d979b647cbc16ed9d1acdb5a201c5.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join activities to benefits sleep at night</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/444a683258d3914a7827a7f997af7ace.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/444a683258d3914a7827a7f997af7ace.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your deck</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/35e66ba9b7320b39683badb3cb64f6eb.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/35e66ba9b7320b39683badb3cb64f6eb.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was inspired by my tragic insomnia experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play cards at night to fall asleep as quick as possible, and enhance your deck by joining activities. Switch cards you have between deck and backups to build the perfect deck to overcome insomnia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a Single Player Rougelike Deckbuilder includes 1 playable character. Player's goal is to reduce their soberness at Night by spending time to play cards. Player can also use stamina joining Activities to gain more cards and advantages at the Daytime after every Night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also face even more Challenge in Deep Dream Mode where game gets harder everyday!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect various cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/3c921834216a30ee8faf03552f5cb368.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/3c921834216a30ee8faf03552f5cb368.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer Insomnia </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras/680d979b647cbc16ed9d1acdb5a201c5.avif?t=1742666461\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265130/extras_big/680d979b647cbc16ed9d1acdb5a201c5.avif?t=1742666461 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join activities to benefits sleep at night</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src